<BR>
Amazingly enough, he gave the bracer over to the guy in our group who was attacked first, and was killed, by Petrifin.  We all rolled random, including the monk (I gotta get his name from my logs to give him the credit he is due..).  It was won by our Druid.<BR>
<BR>
I was hoping to get it off the Druid for some pp - but after seeing that it's never sold and that one guy traded it for a Ykesha I doubt he'll part with it.<BR>
